    chronologyEn: [
      'Okuninushi cedes the land of Izumo to the heavenly gods in the kuniyuzuri.',
      'Amaterasu commands her grandson Ninigi to descend and rule the earth.',
      'Amaterasu bestows the Three Sacred Treasures: the mirror Yata-no-Kagami, the sword Kusanagi, and the jewel Magatama.',
      'Ninigi descends with a retinue of gods and arrives atop Mount Takachiho.',
      'Ninigi establishes his palace at Takachiho after declaring the site perfect.',
